§4§l     §4§l§nThe Story§0
§0
§7       by Bonkill
#- At first there was nothing.§0
§0
§0Only a cosmic storm of duping and jajapvpers on a now dead server.§0
§0
§0And then an idea popped into Bonkill's head.§0
§0
§0What if I made my own server, with sharding, and hookers.
#- And so it was done.§0
§0
§0It was called /r/Devoted, mainly because Bonkill had squated on that subreddit.§0
§0
§0But also because he wanted to make a happy place for autistic children to spend their lives on instead of going outside.
#- He asked his civ-dad ProgrammerDan to help him.§0
§0
§0And so there was spigot.§0
§0
§0And from that came Devoted 1.0 which everyone agrees was a silly experiment.§0
§0
§0Then Devoted 2.0 launched.
#- It was much better and had less sharding.§0
§0
§0But it was just Devoted bro.§0
§0
§0And then, this world was born... and it was good.
#- 
§0
§0
§0
§4§l  §2§l§nFurry Simplicity§0
§0
§7   by greenthing518
#-      Once upon a time,§0
§0a cat once laid eyes on a quarry mine. He said "What a nice hole. I think Imma go double click to pick!" The cat went home to get his pickaxe and realized, "Wow! my house is an ugly ass white box." His new realization urged him to 
#- make an attempt at architecture. His trial ended in complete error. For he is an error.§0
§0     After the cat failed to build something other than a pale cube, he went to go mine in that hole he found. "Time to go double click to pick!" he joyfully spouted
#- as he strolled into the quarry. Though, his limited intellegence did not alarm him of the height of the hole before he decided to jump to the bottom to get there quicker. Or because he hates himself. Either way he died because he's an animal fucking peice
#- gay trash. XOXO - G§0
§0(To J)
#- 
§0
§0
§0
§4§l  §5§l§nMalen Fight Song§0
§0
§7   by FabledMrFox
#- Like an ulcer;§0
§0Inside my colon;§0
§0Sending big pain;§0
§0Into my colon;§0
§0Like how a single word;§0
§0Can be followed by a colon;§0
§0I might have only one ass;§0
§0But it will make an explosion.
#- And all those pills I didn't take;§0
§0Ritalin inside by brain;§0
§0I will PvP tonight;§0
§0Can you hear my voice this time?§0

#- This is my fight song;§0
§0Smoke with my dad song;§0
§0Prove I don't have Crohn's;§0
§0My addy's turned on;§0
§0Starting right now, I'll be stong;§0
§0I'll smoke my dad's bong;§0
§0And I don't care if nobody else believes;§0

#- Cause I've still got 30 guys from HCTeams.§0
§0
§0
