§5§l      §9§l§nRegrets§0
§0
§7   by Saren_Solaris
#- My soul, burnt black§0
§0
§0Old memories come back§0
§0
§0My past, Wont leave me§0
§0
§0Only the end will free me§0
§0

#- Deep hurt, My pain§0
§0
§0All the regret makes me insane§0
§0
§0My eyes, wet§0
§0The reasons why, Ill never forget§0
§0
§0My arms, bloody§0
§0My words, cunning§0
§0My heart, broken§0
§0On each breath, Im choking
#- 
